project: ''Once upon a time, in a world oppressed by a powerful system, three warriors—Suli4Q, Tech N9ne, and 2Gunn Kevi—rose up to fight back. Suli4Q’s words sparked hope, Tech N9ne’s rhymes struck fear into their enemies, and 2Gunn Kevi’s fearless spirit inspired resistance. Alone, they had faced the system’s grip, but together, they formed an unstoppable force. United by music, grit, and determination, they vowed to tear down the walls of control.''
